'''''The Art of Ralph McQuarrie''''' is a 400-page book showcasing the artwork of ''[[Star Wars]]'' concept artist [[Ralph McQuarrie]]. Limited to a release of 2,000 copies, this book was published by [[Dreams and Visions Press]] in [[April]] [[2007]] and debuted at [[Celebration IV]] on [[May 24]]-[[May 28|28]], 2007.

The 2,000-copy limited edition publication consists of:
*1,625 unsigned, slipcased hardcovers
*300 (250 numbered copies for sale) slipcased hardcovers signed by Ralph McQuarrie, [[Doug Chiang]] and [[Ken Ralston]]
*75 (52 lettered for sale) leatherbound hardcovers in deluxe presentation boxes signed by Ralph McQuarrie, Doug Chiang, Ken Ralston and [[Anthony Daniels]]

